      <title>美国财政部将本季度借款预期下调至 5460 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/us-treasury-trims-borrowing-estimate-to-546-billion-for-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部下调了本季度联邦借款预期，但仍预计年底（联邦债务上限重新生效之前）的现金余额将达到 7000 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/us-treasury-trims-borrowing-estimate-to-546-billion-for-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
